n+m=0, 1, 2, 3, or 4; and 
B and B′ are each independently a purine residue or a pyrimidine residue linked through the 9- or 1-position, respectively; 
Z=OH or N3; 
Z′=OH or N3; 
Y=H or OH; 
Y′=H or OH; 
provided that when Z is N3, Y is H or when Z′ is N3, Y′ is H; or 


